He has performed worldwide with his group and recorded 15 CDs as a leader, collaborating with numerous jazz and pop stars including Benny Golson, Sting, Steve Grossman, Eric Clapton, Dave Liebman, and Bjork. The performance will also showcase ingenious pianism.
